summary: Fixes a bug that occurs when Skyrim Medieval Economy is installed with Realistic Needs and Diseases.
descriptionHtml:
This mod \'fixes\' a problem that occurs when you have Skyrim Medieval Economy installed with Realistic Needs and Diseases. When both of these mods are installed together, the innkeepers buy/sell lists are empty. This mod simply restores the vanilla buy/sell lists so the RND food items are back.

Released with the blessing of the mod author, who is busy finishing the mod.
author: 0kamikaze
